            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Joshua.24:1-33",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJoshua%2024%3A1-33%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_1%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJoshua%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Covenant%20Renewed%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Joshua%20summoned%20all%20the%20tribes%20of%20Israel%20to%20Shechem%2C%20including%20their%20elders%2C%20leaders%2C%20judges%2C%20and%20officers.%20So%20they%20came%20and%20presented%20themselves%20to%20God.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_2%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EJoshua%20said%20to%20the%20people%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%3A%20Long%20ago%20your%20ancestors%2C%20including%20Terah%2C%20the%20father%20of%20Abraham%20and%20Nahor%2C%20lived%20beyond%20the%20Euphrates%20River%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E24%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20river%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2024%3A3%2C%2014%2C%2015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20they%20worshiped%20other%20gods.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_3%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20I%20took%20your%20ancestor%20Abraham%20from%20the%20land%20beyond%20the%20Euphrates%20and%20led%20him%20into%20the%20land%20of%20Canaan.%20I%20gave%20him%20many%20descendants%20through%20his%20son%20Isaac.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_4%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3ETo%20Isaac%20I%20gave%20Jacob%20and%20Esau.%20To%20Esau%20I%20gave%20the%20mountains%20of%20Seir%2C%20while%20Jacob%20and%20his%20children%20went%20down%20into%20Egypt.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_5%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThen%20I%20sent%20Moses%20and%20Aaron%2C%20and%20I%20brought%20terrible%20plagues%20on%20Egypt%3B%20and%20afterward%20I%20brought%20you%20out%20as%20a%20free%20people.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_6%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20when%20your%20ancestors%20arrived%20at%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E24%3A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Esea%20of%20reeds.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20Egyptians%20chased%20after%20you%20with%20chariots%20and%20charioteers.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_7%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20your%20ancestors%20cried%20out%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20I%20put%20darkness%20between%20you%20and%20the%20Egyptians.%20I%20brought%20the%20sea%20crashing%20down%20on%20the%20Egyptians%2C%20drowning%20them.%20With%20your%20very%20own%20eyes%20you%20saw%20what%20I%20did.%20Then%20you%20lived%20in%20the%20wilderness%20for%20many%20years.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_8%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BFinally%2C%20I%20brought%20you%20into%20the%20land%20of%20the%20Amorites%20on%20the%20east%20side%20of%20the%20Jordan.%20They%20fought%20against%20you%2C%20but%20I%20destroyed%20them%20before%20you.%20I%20gave%20you%20victory%20over%20them%2C%20and%20you%20took%20possession%20of%20their%20land.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_9%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Balak%20son%20of%20Zippor%2C%20king%20of%20Moab%2C%20started%20a%20war%20against%20Israel.%20He%20summoned%20Balaam%20son%20of%20Beor%20to%20curse%20you%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_10%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3Ebut%20I%20would%20not%20listen%20to%20him.%20Instead%2C%20I%20made%20Balaam%20bless%20you%2C%20and%20so%20I%20rescued%20you%20from%20Balak.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_11%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhen%20you%20crossed%20the%20Jordan%20River%20and%20came%20to%20Jericho%2C%20the%20men%20of%20Jericho%20fought%20against%20you%2C%20as%20did%20the%20Amorites%2C%20the%20Perizzites%2C%20the%20Canaanites%2C%20the%20Hittites%2C%20the%20Girgashites%2C%20the%20Hivites%2C%20and%20the%20Jebusites.%20But%20I%20gave%20you%20victory%20over%20them.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_12%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20I%20sent%20terror%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E24%3A12%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Often%20rendered%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20hornet.%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20meaning%20of%20the%20Hebrew%20is%20uncertain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20ahead%20of%20you%20to%20drive%20out%20the%20two%20kings%20of%20the%20Amorites.%20It%20was%20not%20your%20swords%20or%20bows%20that%20brought%20you%20victory.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_13%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20gave%20you%20land%20you%20had%20not%20worked%20on%2C%20and%20I%20gave%20you%20towns%20you%20did%20not%20build%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20towns%20where%20you%20are%20now%20living.%20I%20gave%20you%20vineyards%20and%20olive%20groves%20for%20food%2C%20though%20you%20did%20not%20plant%20them.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_14%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSo%20fear%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20serve%20him%20wholeheartedly.%20Put%20away%20forever%20the%20idols%20your%20ancestors%20worshiped%20when%20they%20lived%20beyond%20the%20Euphrates%20River%20and%20in%20Egypt.%20Serve%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20alone.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_15%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20if%20you%20refuse%20to%20serve%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20then%20choose%20today%20whom%20you%20will%20serve.%20Would%20you%20prefer%20the%20gods%20your%20ancestors%20served%20beyond%20the%20Euphrates%3F%20Or%20will%20it%20be%20the%20gods%20of%20the%20Amorites%20in%20whose%20land%20you%20now%20live%3F%20But%20as%20for%20me%20and%20my%20family%2C%20we%20will%20serve%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_16%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20people%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWe%20would%20never%20abandon%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20serve%20other%20gods.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_17%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20our%20God%20is%20the%20one%20who%20rescued%20us%20and%20our%20ancestors%20from%20slavery%20in%20the%20land%20of%20Egypt.%20He%20performed%20mighty%20miracles%20before%20our%20very%20eyes.%20As%20we%20traveled%20through%20the%20wilderness%20among%20our%20enemies%2C%20he%20preserved%20us.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_18%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20was%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20who%20drove%20out%20the%20Amorites%20and%20the%20other%20nations%20living%20here%20in%20the%20land.%20So%20we%2C%20too%2C%20will%20serve%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20for%20he%20alone%20is%20our%20God.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_19%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Joshua%20warned%20the%20people%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BYou%20are%20not%20able%20to%20serve%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20for%20he%20is%20a%20holy%20and%20jealous%20God.%20He%20will%20not%20forgive%20your%20rebellion%20and%20your%20sins.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_20%22%20bk%3D%22josh%22%20ch%3D%2224%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20you%20abandon%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20serve%20other%20gods%2C%20he%20will%20turn%20against%20you%20and%20destroy%20you%2C%20even%20though%20he%20has%20been%20so%20good%20to%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22josh_24_21